Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Watergate: Nixon's changing stories, 1973
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqlv5
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 26 May 1973
A question of clarity. A week of presidential explanation, in the guise of polysyllabic obfuscation, over the Watergate scandal.